Sentencas: Microstructure development in (LaxSr1-x)MnO3 (LSMO) ceramics were investigated.
Grains of size less than 0.5 mum formed small lumps (<3 mum) in porous LSMO ceramics with x = 0.25 and 0.3.
Grain sizes are evidently larger at 1400degreesC/h than LSMO ceramics of x = 0.25-0.35 sintered at 1300degreesC/4 h. Atx = 0.4, grain size did not increase with sintering temperature visibly.
Grain size decreased with increased lanthanum content.
